404
00:37:01,780 --> 00:37:07,360
[SPEAKER_01] I on postane predsjednik i započne četiri rata, pogine milijon i pol ljudi.

405
00:37:07,360 --> 00:37:10,139
[SPEAKER_01] I niko o tome ništa ne raspravlja.

406
00:37:10,139 --> 00:37:17,380
